Grub Settings:
git clone https://github.com/vinceliuice/grub2-themes.git
sudo nano /etc/default/grub
change rows to:
GRUB_TERMINAL_OUTPUT="gfxterm"
GRUB_ENABLE_BLSCFG = false
GRUB_DEFAULT="saved"
GRUB_SAVEDEFAULT=true
sudo ./install.sh -t tela -s 4k

for change os names:
sudo dnf install grub-customizer
grub-customizer

fix /EFI/fedora/grubenv’ not found:
sudo dnf -y reinstall grub2-common
sudo grub2-editenv create
sudo grub2-mkconfig -o /boot/grub2/grub.cfg
sudo dracut -f --regenerate-all

Дополнительный команды, если ни промогает:
sudo find /boot -iname '*grub*.cfg'
sudo grub2-mkconfig -o /boot/grub2/grub.cfg
sudo grub2-mkconfig -o /boot/efi/EFI/fedora/grub.cfg

sudo mv /etc/grub.d/ /etc/grub.d_backup/
sudo dnf reinstall grub2-tools -y
sudo grub2-mkconfig -o /boot/grub2/grub.cfg


